registerPredSymbol

public NodeBuilder.PredSymbol registerPredSymbol(java.lang.String name,
                                                 NodeBuilder.Sort[] args)
All the symbols are scoped by the push/isValid calls. All symbols registered prior to push/isValid call, are assumed to be used only by the formula passed there, and possibly by stuff further up the stack. In other words, they become invalid after pop or the end of isValid call respectively.

args -
